<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb6d22809-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2"><num value="300ii–2">§ 300ii–2.</num><heading> National lifespan respite resource center</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idb6d2280a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Establishment</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may award a grant or cooperative agreement to a public or private nonprofit entity to establish a National Resource Center on Lifespan Respite Care (referred to in this section as the “center”).</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idb6d2280b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Purposes of the center</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The center shall—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb6d2280c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2/b/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> maintain a national database on lifespan respite care;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb6d2280d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2/b/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> provide training and technical assistance to State, community, and nonprofit respite care programs; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idb6d2280e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s300ii–2/b/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> provide information, referral, and educational programs to the public on lifespan respite care.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idb6d2280f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373">July 1, 1944, ch. 373</ref>, title XXIX, § 2903, as added <ref href="/us/pl/109/442/s2">Pub. L. 109–442, § 2</ref>, <date date="2006-12-21">Dec. 21, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3295">120 Stat. 3295</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
